{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PointerEvent.tiltX","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltX","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Pointer_events\">Pointer events</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/isPrimary\"><code>isPrimary</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerId\"><code>pointerId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerType\"><code>pointerType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pressure\"><code>pressure</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tangentialPressure\"><code>tangentialPressure</code></a></li><li><em><code>tiltX</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltY\"><code>tiltY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/twist\"><code>twist</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/getCoalescedEvents\"><code>getCoalescedEvents()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Pointer Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/releasePointerCapture\"><code>Element.releasePointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/setPointerCapture\"><code>Element.setPointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/maxTouchPoints\"><code>Navigator.maxTouchPoints</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>tiltX</code></strong> read-only property of the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a> interface is the angle (in degrees) between the <em>Y-Z\nplane</em> of the pointer and the screen. This property is typically only useful for a\n  pen/stylus pointer type.\n</p>\n<p>For an illustration of this property see <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/pointerevents/#dom-pointerevent-tiltx\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Figure 2 in the specification</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The angle in degrees between the Y-Z plane of the pointer (stylus) and the screen. The range of values is <code>-90</code> to <code>90</code>, inclusive, where a positive value is a tilt to the right. For devices that do not support this property, the value is <code>0</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  This example illustrates simple accessing of the <code>tiltX</code> and\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltY\" title=\"tiltY\"><code>tiltY</code></a> properties.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>someElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"pointerdown\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">process_tilt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tiltX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tiltY<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/pointerevents/#dom-pointerevent-tiltx","title":"Pointer Events"}],"query":"api.PointerEvent.tiltX"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PointerEvent.tiltX","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltX/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The tiltX read-only property of the\n  PointerEvent interface is the angle (in degrees) between the Y-Z\nplane of the pointer and the screen. This property is typically only useful for a\n  pen/stylus pointer type.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:17:24.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PointerEvent.tiltX","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/pointerevent/tiltx","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/pointerevent/tiltx/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/4b4638246aad5d39b9a2e5c572b179b4c39c0a84","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent","title":"PointerEvent"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltX","title":"PointerEvent.tiltX"}],"pageTitle":"PointerEvent.tiltX - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}